<doc f='llvm/lld/ELF/SyntheticSections.cpp' l='2370'>// This function writes a 2-bit bloom filter. This bloom filter alone
// usually filters out 80% or more of all symbol lookups [1].
// The dynamic linker uses the hash table only when a symbol is not
// filtered out by a bloom filter.
//
// [1] Ulrich Drepper (2011), &quot;How To Write Shared Libraries&quot; (Ver. 4.1.2),
//     p.9, https://www.akkadia.org/drepper/dsohowto.pdf</doc>
